1. On je *lažno* obećao da će doći na sastanak. (He falsely promised to come to the meeting.)
2. *Lažno* je optužen za krađu. (He was falsely accused of theft.)
3. Njihov osmeh je *lažan*. (Their smile is fake.)
4. *Lažni* računi su otkriveni tokom istrage. (Fake invoices were discovered during the investigation.)
5. Potpisao je ugovor *lažno* ime. (He signed the contract with a false name.)
6. *Lažni* doktor je bio uhapšen zbog zloupotrebe titule. (A fake doctor was arrested for misuse of the title.)
7. Njegov osmeh je *lažan* kao i njegova obećanja. (His smile is as fake as his promises.)
8. Ona je *lažno* tvrdila da nije videla incident. (She falsely claimed that she didn't see the incident.)
9. *Lažne* vesti su postale veliki problem u današnjem svetu. (Fake news has become a big problem in today's world.)
10. Njegova slika na internetu je *lažna*. (His picture on the internet is fake.)